  _description: A battle-hardened veteran who has survived countless campaigns across
    hostile sectors. Garrett relies not on complex tactics, but on endurance, discipline,
    and the ability to hold the line under overwhelming pressure. His combat style
    revolves around survival, battlefield control through presence, and gradual suppression
    of enemy efficiency rather than direct aggression.
